Uru Eke (amụrụ n'October 11, 1979) bụ onye Naijirịa na-eme ihe nkiri na onye na-emepụta ihe nkiri
A maara ya maka mmepụta mbụ ya "Cheta M", ọrụ ya dị ka Obi na usoro weebụ na-ewu ewu nke Ndani TV Rumour Has It

Last Flight to Abuja, Africa Magic's Drama series BABY Drama na ihe nkiri ya nke abụọ dị ka onye na-emepụta ihe a na-akpọ For Old Times' Sake Onye na-eme ihe nkiri ahụ, onye bụ ọkachamara IT tupu ọ banye Nollywood, ka na-ekerịta oge ya n'etiti ụlọ ọrụ ntụrụndụ na ụwa Tech.

Eke bụ nwa Mbaise nke Imo Steetị, South-Eastern Niajirịa, mana a mụrụ ya na Newham, East London na United Kingdom. Ọ gụrụ akwụkwọ na Galleywall Infants School, London, tupu ọ kwaga Naịjirịa ebe ọ gara Gideon Comprehensive High School maka agụmakwụkwọ ụlọ akwụkwọ sekọndrị ya
N'ịga n'ihu na agụmakwụkwọ ya, ọ laghachiri London wee gaa Lewisham College tupu ọ gaa Mahadum Greenwich ebe ọ gụrụ Business Information Technology.
Ọ malitere ọrụ ya dị ka onye ndụmọdụ IT na Zurich Insurance Group wee gaa n'ihu na-arụ ọrụ n'ọtụtụ ụlọ ọrụ ego na UK. Uru gbanwere ọrụ na 2011 ma gaa n'ihu na-eme ihe nkiri n'ọtụtụ ihe nkiri.
